  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n218/mode/1up">215</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. mēṟkūṟappaṭṭa āṟaṉuḷ, ikumuñ ciṉṉum paṭarkkaiccollōṭun taṉmaiccollōṭum poruntu nilaiyuṭaiyaveṉa eytiyataṉmēṟciṟappuviti vakuttavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m. 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘kaṇṭiku mallamō’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m. 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘kaṇṇum paṭumō veṉṟiciṉ yāṉē.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m. taṉmaikkaṇ vantaṉa.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Cena-cit3">
        <l>‘pukaḻntiku mallarō peritē.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Cena-cit4">
        <l>‘yāraḵ taṟintici ṉōrē.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m. paṭarkkaikkaṇ vantaṉa.	(27)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/300/mode/1up">300</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/301/mode/1up">301</ref>.</p>

      <p>
‘ikum, ciṉ’ eṉpavaṟṟiṟkup puṟaṉaṭai
      </p>
      <lg>
          <l>avaṟṟuḷ,</l>
          <l>ikumuñ ciṉṉu mēṉai yiṭattoṭun</l>
          <l>takunilai yuṭaiya veṉmaṉār pulavar.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
itu, mēlataṟkup puṟanaṭai kūṟukiṉṟatu,
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ.) avaṟṟu ḷikumum ciṉṉum ― muṟkūṟiya vāṟaṉuḷ ikumum ciṉṉum, ēṉai yiṭattoṭun takunilaiyuṭaiya veṉmaṉār pulavar-oḻinta taṉmaiccollōṭum paṭarkkaic collōṭum poruntum nilaimai yuṭaiya veṉṟu kūṟuvar pulavareṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m.)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘kaṇṭikkum allamō!</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>kaṇṇum paṭumō eṉṟiciṉ yāṉē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉat taṉmaik kaṇṇum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit3">
        <l>‘pukaḻntiku mallarō peritē’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit4">
        <l>‘yāraḵ taṟintici ṉōrē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉappaṭarkkaik kaṇṇum vantaṉa.
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
murukāṟṟuppaṭaiyuḷ,
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit5">
        <l>‘viḷiviṉ</l>
        <l>ṟiruḷniṟa munnīr vaḷaiiya ulakat</l>
        <l>torunī yākit tōṉṟa viḻumiya</l>
        <l>peṟalarum parici ṉalkumati palavuṭaṉ</l>
        <l><gap quantity="5" unit="character" reason="lost"/> malaikiḻavōṉe’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa mati paṭarkkaikkaṇṇum vantataṉait ‘takunilai yuṭaiya’ eṉṟataṉā ṉātal,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit6">
        <l>‘avvac colliṟ kavai yavai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṉuñ cūttirattāṉātal amaittukkoḷka. aṉṟi, matiyai yaṟivākkip pala aṟivuṭaṉē nī yoruvaṉēyākap parici ṉalkumeṉap poruḷ kūṟuvārumuḷar.
      </p>
      <p>
‘ūṉu mūṇu muṉaiyi, ṉeṉṉum paṟuppāṭṭiṉuṭ
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Nacc-cit7">
        <l>‘ceṉmō peruma! vem viḻavuṭai nāṭṭeṉa’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpataṉaiyun taṉmaikkaṇ ‘mō’ varum eṉa ivvāṟamaittalu moṉṟu. aṉṟip ‘peruma’, em viḻavuṭai nāṭṭē nī cel,leṉṟu cuṟṟattār talaivaṉai nōkkikkūṟa, apporunaṉum pāṭṭuṭait talaivaṉai nōkkip piṉṉun kūṟiṉā ṉākap poruḷ kūṟutalu moṉṟu.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n184/mode/1up">177</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n185/mode/1up">178</ref>.</p>
      <p>
eytiyataṉmēṟ ciṟappu viti vakuttalai uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ: ― mēṟ collappaṭṭavaṟṟuḷ ikumum, ciṉṉum taṉmaiyiṉum, paṭarkkaiyiṉum varutal takunilai yuṭaitteṉṟu colluvar. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u–m: ― 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Tey-cit1">
        <l>“kaṇṭiku mallamō yāmē.”</l>
        <trailer>(aiṅkuṟu - 121)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Tey-cit2">
        <l>“kaṇṇum paṭumō yeṉṟiciṉ yāṉē”</l>
        <trailer>(naṟ - 61)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
ivai kaṇṭēm, eṉṟēṉ eṉṉum poruṭkaṇ vantaṉa.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Tey-cit3">
        <l>“pukaḻntiku mallarō peritē-</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Tey-cit4">
        <l>pāṭal cāṉṟa viṟalvēn taṉummē”.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Tey-cit5">
        <l>“veṟpuṭaiya varaṇ kaṭantu</l>
        <l>tuppuṟuvar puṟam peṟṟiciṉē.”</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC275-Tey-cit6">
        <l>“yāraḵ taṟintici ṉōrē”.</l>
        <trailer>(kuṟun - 18)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉap pāl kāṭṭum eḻuttōṭu aṭuttuvarutaluṅ koḷka.	[26]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
